{"results":[{"aya":"197","id":3129,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"以色列后裔中的学者们知道它，这难道还不可以做他们一个迹象吗？","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"198","id":3130,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"假若我把它降示一个非阿拉伯人，","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"199","id":3131,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"而那个人对他们宣读它，那末，他们绝不会信仰它。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"200","id":3132,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"我这样使犯罪的人常怀否认的意念。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"201","id":3133,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"他们不信仰它，直到他们看见痛苦的刑罚。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"202","id":3134,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"那种刑罚将在他们不知不觉的时候，忽然降临他们。","translator":"Ma Jian"},{"aya":"203","id":3135,"locale":"zh","sura":"026","text":"他们将说：我们将蒙宽限吗？","translator":"Ma Jian"}],"metadata":{"itemsPerPage":7,"pages":33,"previousPage":"/zh/s026-28.json","nextPage":"/zh/s026-30.json"}}